  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nThe wallet is unresponsive on windows. It seems to be ok on linux and macOS.\r\nPlease see the video for reference:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/47811206/75ef1835-58f0-405c-9d45-b47588432c52\r\n\r\nThe purpose of this task is to analyse and improve the performance when opening the wallet on windows.\r\n\r\n<!-- Provide a short description describing the problem you are experiencing. -->\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n1. Open the app\r\n2. Make sure you have a wallet account with some assets and collectibles\r\n3. Open the wallet\r\n<!-- example: step 1. do X step 2. do Y etc.. -->\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nThe wallet is responsive and the app doesn't freeze\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nThe wallet is unresponsive, the app is freezing.\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Operating System: Windows\r\n\r\n",
